{"tid":1165763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子交易廣場天台企跳獲救送院","createTime":"2019-05-22T04:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T04:30:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13338ec48ad0f05016d7432071bb27cc6ab0595d","tid":1165763,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"中環交易廣場2期，今早10時半，一名年約30歲身穿筆挺恤衫西褲的男子，被發現在大廈天台危險位置徘徊，警方及消防接報到場時，男子已自行返回安全位置，雖然他的情緒未見激動，但仍將他送院檢查。據悉，有人因感到不開心，才走上天台。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=1747a40d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190522/59627977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627977&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=01dc6db8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190522%2F59627977&h=cbd73650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190522/59627977</a>"},{"pid":"59f3086abeabb2b59cc877184a60cef8dd948249","tid":1165763,"uid":132210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"真係會自殺既人多數都無咁多花款"},{"pid":"0e4615b3f50969db10fe599a08ed402461717be6","tid":1165763,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"霸定位先<br />\n<br />\n之後3250億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2575965951869c0d3b635c0c8f0ae52b9f3d88","tid":116